Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:41.47,Title,TOP LEFT SIGN,0,0,0,,{\frz10.2\pos(360,380)\3c&H7C7A7F&}المَغطس
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:41.47,Title,TOP RIGHT SIGN,0,0,0,,{\frz9.846\pos(524,346)\3c&H7C7A7F&}المَكتبة
